cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation and superpixels. It also leverages deep networks for learning superpixel segmentation, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of flexible loss functions and end-to-end training suggests that it may also belong to the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the mention of downstream integration with deep networks suggests that it may also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
